      • getOptionalElements

        @NonNull
 @Deprecated
public java.lang.String[] getOptionalElements()
        Deprecated. 
        Array of elements that are not part of AAMVA standard and are specific to each US state. If no specific elements existed inside 2D barcode, this is an empty array. Otherwise, this array contains list of state-specific elements in the same order as given inside barcode. NOTE: Size of this array is both state-specific and barcode-specific. Each US state has ability to arbitrarily define size and contents of these elements. You can obtain the US state with UsdlRecognizer.Result.getField(UsdlKeys) and using UsdlKeys.IssuingJurisdictionName as a parameter.
